{
  "stem": "10862.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just said I don't know what happened to those children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And eventually, of course, all the mothers learned the fate of the children because the children never came back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the first night when we arrived at Czestochowa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the following day we had to get up again for the appel and counting and giving us new numbers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had an ammunition factory, a bullet factory, and all the women and the men worked in the bullet factory, but not together.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked with my sisters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I used to do-- and at that time I already had to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was already older, and I was picking up the bullets that fell out of the machines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As they were making the bullets, sometimes a bullet that was not a perfect bullet would fall out, and I had to gather up all those bullets on the machine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day I remember while I was being in the factory, my sister, Anne, my sister Hannah, older sister, her machine got stuck.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The bullets got stuck in one of the machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the kapo, the woman that was there, the kapo, took my sister aside and gave her 20 lashes with a-- with a, a leather strap right in front of everybody because her machine got stuck.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Not that she could help it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It wasn't her fault, but she punished her right away because her machine was not working.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And finally they were able to fix the machine and, of course, the bullets started coming.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this was my-- pretty much for a whole year, we did that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We worked in the-- in the factory making bullets.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And life in there too was very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
